Date: 1997-03-31

Title: Seeking an Even-Parity Mass Term for 3-D Gauge Theory

Authors: R. Jackiw and S-Y. Pi

Comments: 11 pages, revtex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B403 (1997) 297-303

Mass-gap calculations in three-dimensional gauge theories are discussed. Alsowe present a Chern--Simons-like mass-generating mechanism which preservesparity and is realized non-perturbatively.